contentrichtext.text: '''''[http://en.wikipedia.org/w/wiki.phtml?title=MediaWiki:VfD-Wikipedia:Articles_requested_for_more_than_two_years&action=edit Add to this debate.]''''' This page is empty and serves no point. --[[User:Alex S|Alex S]] 03:46, 27 Mar 2004 (UTC) Keep. It is only empty because it has been successful and all such requests have been cleared up. This page has been a useful tool in the past, with many requests cleared up, and will again be useful in the future. Within a few weeks there will be a bunch more two year old requests, and they shall then be added to this page. - [[User:SimonP|SimonP]] 07:22, Mar 27, 2004 (UTC) :Good point. Retracting. --[[User:Alex S|Alex S]] 17:53, 27 Mar 2004 (UTC)
